name: Hibbert Smith
description: Well, let’s see… I’ve been told that I’m hard to read…. I find it easier to forgive than to forget. I’m a sucker for a woman with a great sense of humor. I’m too logical for my own good. I’m independent and strong~willed,romantic at heart but hard~core on the surface. I don’t trust quickly but when I do, I trust fully. I believe that jealousy is idiocy. Negative people annoy me. I’ve served and lived in many contries. I judge myself more than others. I believe more love and honesty don’t fall easliy. My favorite ice~cream is Rocky Road. My life is absolutely filled with amazing people expecially my son Christhoper.
